{"tid":2071558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警指示威者無叫口號「可能啞啩」","createTime":"2020-06-20T02:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T03:04:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2fae6b11484060b8ac9507f226092133ec06737b","tid":2071558,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/7TUTMVRMQXI3B623MW3YGBNVC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2F7TUTMVRMQXI3B623MW3YGBNVC4%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3O%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=ef775445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2F7TUTMVRMQXI3B623MW3YGBNVC4%2F&h=8ce6a7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/7TUTMVRMQXI3B623MW3YGBNVC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警指示威者無叫口號「可能啞啩」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【貼紙襲警案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年聖誕假期各區商場發起「和你Shop」，一名年輕地產經紀在尖沙嘴海港城內，把一張寫上「感謝你哋嘅默默耕耘」的紙張貼在沒戴委任證的便衣警背脊，被控襲警，案件昨續審。負責拘捕被告的便衣警不認為自己打扮似途人，指市民憑感覺可識別警員身份，正如他和同袍當日沒叫口號已被認出是警員；若有示威者沒叫口號，他說：「可能佢哋啞啩，聾啞人士都有。」<br />\n<br />\n油尖警區重案組高級警。。。。。被告時有展示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6IAUW3MQ6NITCDVX774BEVCWQQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6IAUW3MQ6NITCDVX774BEVCWQQ.gif&h=698c27a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油尖警區重案組高級警員林志輝（左圖）昨稱看見被告何曉朗（右圖）用力拍打案中警長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱可憑感覺辨別便衣<br />\n<br />\n林當日身穿淺藍色上衣，辯方問他，市民如何分辨警員及示威者，林稱：「冇區分㗎，有人犯法就要拉，冇話身穿咩色衫。」他不同意他當日的打扮與途人相似，辯方問：「即係任何人一望你哋，就知你哋係警員？」林答：「要憑佢哋嘅感覺。」又自言當日沒叫口號，但已有人識別出他們是警員。<br />\n<br />\n辯方問：「冇叫口號就係警員，咁有啲示威者冇叫口號，咁佢哋係咩呀？」林稱：「可能佢哋啞啩，聾啞人士都有。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方播片，片段顯示被告遭制服時，左手套住一卷膠紙圈，林承認沒檢取膠紙圈，「我覺得當時佢手上冇膠紙圈喺度。」。。。。。押後至6月24日續審。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC3043/19"},{"pid":"ad00d10635ac279ec3e9310b2ba258728d671367","tid":2071558,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"我淨係班狗一定係弱智<br />\n全部上庭講d野唔係正常人mindset講得出"},{"pid":"91fa79816099c00569dc3fe5dae77c6cb9e0d2f1","tid":2071558,"uid":99725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"離遠都聞到浸狗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cc118d2e2ff6d89daa97fbcf2e6f925eec7250","tid":2071558,"uid":165234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"啲證供愈黎愈尻"},{"pid":"de90c45b416b7074c9acd6d0332e6088ec19eafb","tid":2071558,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"自己都兜到亂晒籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400ac6da03feac077abb82c82cf23378796d1e13","tid":2071558,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"憑怎狗除味辨認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd0f6aafd5e5f61f54f8a08fa9c162bf1be71a3","tid":2071558,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />市民要用狗味去認狗隻"},{"pid":"ba4f7b8446eafe54142ad5df59c0984c13d79c97","tid":2071558,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"「係囉<br />\n反警暴反極權大遊行都唔只二百萬㗎<br />\n可能有啲係出唔到街咁解<br />\n計起上黎六百萬都有添」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n照隻狗咁講 我嘅講法應該OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}